# PHOENIX PROTOCOL - UNIFIED GATEWAY CONFIG V3.1 (CORRECTED GATEWAY IP)
# 1. STATUS: Multi-Tenant / Multi-Project Gateway.
# 2. FIX: Updated Juristi reverse_proxy to use the server's actual gateway IP (172.18.0.1).
# 3. ARCHITECTURE: 
#    - Haveri: Routed via internal Docker DNS (backend:8000).
#    - Juristi: Routed via Host Gateway (172.18.0.1:8001).
# 4. SECURITY: Strict Headers maintained for both domains.

